<div class="wp-block-xv-blocks-container subheading-text tw-bg-cover tw-bg-center tw-bg-no-repeat">
<p class="">A <strong>VPN</strong>, or<strong> virtual private network</strong>, is a secure tunnel between your device and the internet. VPNs protect you from snooping, interference, and censorship.<br> <br> As you connect to a secure VPN server, your internet traffic goes through an encrypted tunnel that nobody can see into—including hackers, governments, and your internet service provider. </p>
</div>



