<section class="wp-block-xv-blocks-container block-group tw-bg-cover tw-bg-center tw-bg-no-repeat">
<section class="wp-block-xv-blocks-block-group-heading heading-block"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="column txt-center">
<h2 class="">Benefits and advantages of VPN </h2>
</div></div></div></section>



<section class="wp-block-xv-blocks-container two-col-content-m-block block-right txt-left fixed-width tw-bg-cover tw-bg-center tw-bg-no-repeat"><div class="container">
<div class="wp-block-columns row">
<div class="wp-block-column column-image">
<img loading="lazy" class="img-block wp-block-xv-blocks-advanced-image advanced-image-block img-block" alt="Laptop screens demonstrating the before and after process of changing a user's IP address." height="470" width="470" src="https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/Change_your_location-19581a6ef9c7290333423ed0ee97e3d4.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;cs=srgb&amp;fit=max&amp;q=60&amp;w=320&amp;s=c6cd457fe108c374ecc604998cb69fd3" srcset="https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/Change_your_location-19581a6ef9c7290333423ed0ee97e3d4.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;cs=srgb&amp;fit=max&amp;q=60&amp;w=470&amp;s=575ef53afcf6a2f62b756dff804aff2a 470w,https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/Change_your_location-19581a6ef9c7290333423ed0ee97e3d4.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;cs=srgb&amp;fit=max&amp;q=60&amp;w=940&amp;s=65c2ffbb319d42d3d9609168632f1b4d 940w" style="--image-width: 470px;">
</div>



<div class="wp-block-column column-content">
<div class="wp-block-xv-blocks-container tw-bg-cover tw-bg-center tw-bg-no-repeat">
<h3 class="has-text-align-left">Change your location </h3>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-xv-blocks-container subheading-text tw-bg-cover tw-bg-center tw-bg-no-repeat">
<p class="">Using a VPN <strong>changes your IP address</strong>, the unique number that identifies you and where you are in the world. A new IP address makes it harder to determine your identity and real location. With ExpressVPN, you can appear to be in the UK, U.S., Canada, Australia, or any of <a href="/vpn-server" target="_self">105 countries</a>. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div></section>



<section class="wp-block-xv-blocks-container two-col-content-m-block block-left txt-left fixed-width tw-bg-cover tw-bg-center tw-bg-no-repeat"><div class="container">
<div class="wp-block-columns row">
<div class="wp-block-column column-image">
<img loading="lazy" class="img-block wp-block-xv-blocks-advanced-image advanced-image-block img-block" alt="Download VPN provided the best-in-class 256-bit encryption." height="336" width="320" src="https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/encryption-2fc801604da35f1879fc2f4d5da4443b.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;cs=srgb&amp;fit=max&amp;q=60&amp;w=320&amp;s=bbd79bed04dd6a68062ba328d4e1b8f8" srcset="https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/encryption-2fc801604da35f1879fc2f4d5da4443b.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;cs=srgb&amp;fit=max&amp;q=60&amp;w=320&amp;s=bbd79bed04dd6a68062ba328d4e1b8f8 320w,https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/encryption-2fc801604da35f1879fc2f4d5da4443b.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;cs=srgb&amp;fit=max&amp;q=60&amp;w=640&amp;s=3673ea6784486fd8d1c5f86c473f11c7 640w" style="--image-width: 320px;">
</div>



<div class="wp-block-column column-content">
<div class="wp-block-xv-blocks-container tw-bg-cover tw-bg-center tw-bg-no-repeat">
<h3 class="has-text-align-left">Protect your privacy </h3>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-xv-blocks-container subheading-text tw-bg-cover tw-bg-center tw-bg-no-repeat">
<p class="">Changing your IP address with a VPN helps <strong>shield your identity</strong> from websites, apps, and services that want to track you. Good VPNs also prevent your internet provider, mobile carrier, and anyone else who may be listening from seeing your activity, thanks to a layer of strong encryption. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div></section>



<section class="wp-block-xv-blocks-container two-col-content-m-block block-right txt-left fixed-width tw-bg-cover tw-bg-center tw-bg-no-repeat"><div class="container">
<div class="wp-block-columns row">
<div class="wp-block-column column-image">
<img loading="lazy" class="img-block wp-block-xv-blocks-advanced-image advanced-image-block img-block" alt="Router VPN that covers all devices." height="284" width="370" src="https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/vpn-router-connect-more-devices-1ce009403a96a923bbf96979cdfa78c7.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;cs=srgb&amp;fit=max&amp;q=60&amp;w=320&amp;s=f749263a7c6d3aa0b6b974b24a6cd290" srcset="https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/vpn-router-connect-more-devices-1ce009403a96a923bbf96979cdfa78c7.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;cs=srgb&amp;fit=max&amp;q=60&amp;w=370&amp;s=2594ed718f2f929b4fea1adfc3728dbe 370w,https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/vpn-router-connect-more-devices-1ce009403a96a923bbf96979cdfa78c7.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;cs=srgb&amp;fit=max&amp;q=60&amp;w=740&amp;s=71b91283d820a4a8c17a88672047ac3b 740w" style="--image-width: 370px;">
</div>



<div class="wp-block-column column-content">
<div class="wp-block-xv-blocks-container tw-bg-cover tw-bg-center tw-bg-no-repeat">
<h3 class="has-text-align-left">Increase your security </h3>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-xv-blocks-container subheading-text tw-bg-cover tw-bg-center tw-bg-no-repeat">
<p class="">Using a VPN <strong>protects you from security breaches</strong> in many forms, including packet sniffing, rogue Wi-Fi networks, and man-in-the-middle attacks. Travelers, remote workers, and all kinds of on-the-go individuals use a VPN whenever they’re on an untrusted network like free public Wi-Fi. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div></section>



<section class="wp-block-xv-blocks-container button-block tw-bg-cover tw-bg-center tw-bg-no-repeat"><div class="container">
