<div class="wp-block-xv-blocks-container row tw-bg-cover tw-bg-center tw-bg-no-repeat">
<div class="wp-block-xv-blocks-container column tw-bg-cover tw-bg-center tw-bg-no-repeat">
<h2 class="">When should I use a VPN? </h2>



<div class="wp-block-xv-blocks-container subheading-text tw-bg-cover tw-bg-center tw-bg-no-repeat">
<p class="">If privacy is important to you, you should use a VPN <strong>every time you connect to the internet</strong>. A VPN app runs in the background of your device so it won’t get in the way while you use other apps and browse the internet. And you’ll have peace of mind knowing your privacy is always protected. </p>



<p class="">But here are some situations in which a VPN is especially useful: </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>



