<section class="wp-block-xv-blocks-three-col-cards-container-block three-col-step-block"><div class="container">
<div class="wp-block-xv-blocks-three-col-cards-top-section three-col-step-heading paragraph-text">
<h2 class="">Types of VPN </h2>
</div>



<div class="wp-block-xv-blocks-three-col-cards-feature-section three-col-step-cards">
<div class="wp-block-xv-blocks-three-col-cards-card-item three-col-step-cards-col"><div class="three-col-step-card txt-center">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized is-style-default"><img loading="lazy" src="https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/what-is-vpn-commercial-0cfe9d19bf2ef003833167338074949a.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&cs=srgb&fit=max&w=440&q=60&s=9f70aaa4adb9e2c7dac7db7edd90d176" srcset="https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/what-is-vpn-commercial-0cfe9d19bf2ef003833167338074949a.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&cs=srgb&fit=max&w=440&q=60&s=9f70aaa4adb9e2c7dac7db7edd90d176 440w,https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/what-is-vpn-commercial-0cfe9d19bf2ef003833167338074949a.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&cs=srgb&fit=max&w=720&q=60&s=8dfb5244ea762cf6b87f36c437b650c0 720w" alt="Laptop with a plant and drink." width="440" height="337" class="img-block"></figure>



<h5 class="">Commercial VPN </h5>



<div class="wp-block-common-blocks-background-container-block alignfull custom-container"><div class="" style="max-width:1140px ">
<p class="">A commercial VPN, also called a personal VPN or a consumer VPN, is a private service offered directly to individuals, usually for a fee. </p>



<p class="">ExpressVPN is such a VPN service because it directly caters to the privacy needs of its customers. </p>
</div></div>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-xv-blocks-three-col-cards-card-item three-col-step-cards-col"><div class="three-col-step-card txt-center">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized is-style-default"><img loading="lazy" src="https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/what-is-vpn-corporate-de01c1c30b6e672cf07aebad9215903f.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&cs=srgb&fit=max&w=440&q=60&s=262053a22f94dee5039bb054216655a0" srcset="https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/what-is-vpn-corporate-de01c1c30b6e672cf07aebad9215903f.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&cs=srgb&fit=max&w=440&q=60&s=262053a22f94dee5039bb054216655a0 440w,https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/what-is-vpn-corporate-de01c1c30b6e672cf07aebad9215903f.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&cs=srgb&fit=max&w=720&q=60&s=855114fb64b6b3653f71fd6aa4903b2b 720w" alt="Pie chart. " width="440" height="337" class="img-block"></figure>



<h5 class="">Corporate VPN </h5>



<div class="wp-block-common-blocks-background-container-block alignfull custom-container"><div class="" style="max-width:1140px ">
<p class="">A corporate VPN, also called a business VPN, allows an organization’s remote employees to connect securely to the internet as if they were physically present in the office. </p>



<p class="">Unlike commercial VPNs, however, corporate VPNs are meant to protect the privacy of the company and not necessarily the individual. </p>
</div></div>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-xv-blocks-three-col-cards-card-item three-col-step-cards-col"><div class="three-col-step-card txt-center">
<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized is-style-default"><img loading="lazy" src="https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/what-is-vpn-self-setup-ed5d81dd4ab9d9b38dba7cb4159e6a5e.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&cs=srgb&fit=max&w=440&q=60&s=cc9ce6daea4c008c76de2590c0e90d01" srcset="https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/what-is-vpn-self-setup-ed5d81dd4ab9d9b38dba7cb4159e6a5e.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&cs=srgb&fit=max&w=440&q=60&s=cc9ce6daea4c008c76de2590c0e90d01 440w,https://xv.imgix.net/photos/xv/what-is-vpn-self-setup-ed5d81dd4ab9d9b38dba7cb4159e6a5e.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&cs=srgb&fit=max&w=720&q=60&s=4f169113673ab9da661152977510a62c 720w" alt="Spanner and wrench." width="440" height="337" class="img-block"></figure>



<h5 class="">Self-setup VPN </h5>



<div class="wp-block-common-blocks-background-container-block alignfull custom-container"><div class="" style="max-width:1140px ">
<p class="">Some tech experts and DIY hobbyists choose to set up their own VPN using their own equipment. </p>



<p class="">Self-setup VPNs, however, do not provide the protection of shared IP addresses, server locations in multiple countries, or many other features enjoyed by commercial VPN users. </p>
</div></div>
</div></div>
</div>
</div></section>



